Work's done. I'm leaving first.
We'll catch up later.

584
00:43:37,920 --> 00:43:39,000
Okay.

585
00:44:05,560 --> 00:44:06,400
Puna.

586
00:44:09,440 --> 00:44:10,480
What do you want?

587
00:44:12,520 --> 00:44:13,680
I want to apologize.

588
00:44:14,720 --> 00:44:17,720
I want a chance, one more chance.

589
00:44:18,720 --> 00:44:19,960
A chance for what?

590
00:44:20,760 --> 00:44:24,720
A chance to get to know each other
like before, Puna.

591
00:44:24,800 --> 00:44:26,640
-Please, Puna.
-It's over.

592
00:44:27,640 --> 00:44:29,280
You've destroyed everything.

593
00:44:30,760 --> 00:44:33,240
