597
00:44:44,600 --> 00:44:46,720
I want you to forgive me, Puna.

598
00:44:47,640 --> 00:44:48,760
Please.

599
00:44:50,840 --> 00:44:52,040
I forgive you.

600
00:44:56,280 --> 00:44:57,840
But I won't trust you again.

601
00:45:00,280 --> 00:45:03,880
