to start over? Or…

602
00:45:04,520 --> 00:45:06,360
give me a chance to prove myself again?

603
00:45:15,320 --> 00:45:17,200
Puna, please give me another chance.

604
00:45:25,400 --> 00:45:26,400
Excuse me.

605
00:45:27,040 --> 00:45:28,080
Wait, Puna.

606
00:46:36,280 --> 00:46:37,120
Puna!

607
00:46:38,760 --> 00:46:41,040
What did Mr. Sonrak talk to you about?

608
00:46:41,120 --> 00:46:42,960
He asked for a chance.

609
00:46:43,040 --> 00:46:44,960
And how did you respond?

610
00:46:46,160 --> 00:46:47,840
If it weren't for the teddy bear,

611
00:46:48,640 --> 00:46:50,520
I probably would've slapped him.

612
00:46:50,600 --> 00:46:54,280
This should be handled slowly.
No need to rush.

613
00:46:54,360 --> 00:46:55,880
Hey, come with me.

614
00:46:55,960 --> 00:46:58,920
Some reporters want to interview you.
They're waiting outside.

615
00:46:59,720 --> 00:47:01,160
Reporters for an interview?

616
00:47:01,240 --> 00:47:03,040
About your performance
with Chaiya just now.

617
00:47:03,120 --> 00:47:05,800
It's blowing up on social media.
Everyone's talking about it.

618
00:47:05,880 --> 00:47:07,400
Right now, reporters

619
00:47:07,480 --> 00:47:09,280
are calling Emily's phone

620
00:47:09,360 --> 00:47:11,440
to schedule interviews
with you and Chaiya.

621
00:47:11,520 --> 00:47:13,240
It's gotten that big?

622
00:47:13,320 --> 00:47:16,080
If you want to see how big,
go do the interviews.

623
00:47:24,400 --> 00:47:25,920
I've got the GPS on.

624
00:47:26,000 --> 00:47:27,400
They're coming.

625
00:47:27,480 --> 00:47:29,920
Who? Who's coming?

626
00:47:31,320 --> 00:47:33,960
I came all this way,
and now suddenly you want to cancel?!

627
00:47:34,040 --> 00:47:35,760
It's really necessary, sir.

628
00:47:36,480 --> 00:47:38,520
Necessary? What's necessary?

629
00:47:38,600 --> 00:47:40,080
Are you trying to mess with me?

630
00:47:40,160 --> 00:47:42,040
Then I'd like to search the car.

631
00:47:43,040 --> 00:47:45,480
You're drug dealers!
I'm reporting this to Mr. Singha!

632
00:47:45,560 --> 00:47:47,200
If you think he doesn't know,

633
00:47:48,000 --> 00:47:49,320
go ahead and report us.

634
00:47:50,520 --> 00:47:51,440
Where are you?

635
00:47:51,520 --> 00:47:52,880
Do you want to get yourself killed?
Keep it down!

636
00:47:53,680 --> 00:47:54,840
Ugh!

637
00:47:55,680 --> 00:47:57,760
I've got Village Head Prueng.

638
00:48:01,400 --> 00:48:02,360
You guys.

639
00:48:02,880 --> 00:48:03,920
Get on the helicopter.

640
00:48:06,120 --> 00:48:08,440
That's Maria! Kill her!

